In order to Build the application:
	NodeMon

The following environment variable has to be set up:

  DIMDIR   must be set in "MakeFile"

"DIMDIR" is the main directory of the DIM installation.
For downloading and installing DIM, see www.cern.ch/dim.

Then do:

  make -f Makefile all

NOTE:
The current executable is already in the "linux" directory
and has been built with Debian-linux 2.4.26.

For running the application you must set the environment
variables 
- DIM_DNS_NODE:  node on which dim name server is running
- LD_LIBRARY_PATH: path to the libdim.so of the DIM installation



